{"tid":1857674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本擴大對中國旅遊警示至港澳","createTime":"2020-02-02T09:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T10:51:06.000Z","uid":164771,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"985ea8488dc616030cee8d47ec239309899d0266","tid":1857674,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:42:16.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情蔓延至海外，美國、日本、義大利、法國等相繼出現確診病例。日本表示，因應世衛將武漢肺炎疫情列為「國際突發公共衛生事件」，決定進一定提升對中國的旅遊警示至第二級，當中包括港澳地區，呼籲國民避免前往。首相安倍晉三指，將會提早於明天實施行政命令，把新型冠狀病毒列為「指定傳染病」，若旅客感染病毒將被拒絕入境。<br />\n至於日本接載國民離開武漢的第三架包機，今早返抵東京羽田機場，149人中有8人不適，要送院觀察。此外，現時仍然有日本國民滯留在武漢，當局已經安排大型民用船隻，準備接載他們回國。"},{"pid":"7efc45eeaecd7247e256b1ea1e3e0c47c8838350","tid":1857674,"uid":165361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7873d3d1c4c1b48979db801eea74e2fc112bcbb7","tid":1857674,"uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:42:53.000Z","msg":"遲早到香港"},{"pid":"4973d3110fb9a85e2a760bc971e6adf083f4bd67","tid":1857674,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7f58fc2c840e3c53b8e511ca26bbde44443948","tid":1857674,"uid":285559,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:43:14.000Z","msg":"最衰都係19 唔靜靜地贏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6dd13fac3607635292b2bf6bae4ee75a25b792","tid":1857674,"uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:43:21.000Z","msg":"睇錯限入境"},{"pid":"6eedc34b67bdc1921a2ae